00:40:42,150 --> 00:40:43,090
are you in or not?

861
00:40:44,320 --> 00:40:44,940
Of course, I'm in.

862
00:40:45,400 --> 00:40:46,130
Alright, then.

863
00:40:48,360 --> 00:40:49,340
I really owe you one.

864
00:40:50,480 --> 00:40:51,940
This job of mine,

865
00:40:52,110 --> 00:40:53,460
always dragging things out,
never wrapping up.

866
00:40:53,840 --> 00:40:55,340
So I haven't made it to Beijing yet.

867
00:40:55,840 --> 00:40:57,010
They were about to take me off the list.

868
00:40:57,320 --> 00:40:58,530
The position's saved for his sake.

869
00:40:59,030 --> 00:40:59,460
Brother-in-law,

870
00:40:59,920 --> 00:41:01,530
I've gotta give you a piece of my mind,

871
00:41:02,840 --> 00:41:03,740
why are you so good

872
00:41:04,480 --> 00:41:05,690
at everything?

873
00:41:06,550 --> 00:41:08,260
They've been asking me for you.

874
00:41:08,280 --> 00:41:09,980
If you don't go, they're gonna kill me.

875
00:41:10,710 --> 00:41:11,980
No wonder you're a PhD,

876
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:12,900
a very good talker.

877
00:41:13,280 --> 00:41:14,010
Anyway,

878
00:41:14,670 --> 00:41:15,210
thank you.

879
00:41:15,960 --> 00:41:16,650
Sincerely.

880
00:41:16,880 --> 00:41:17,380
We're family...

881
00:41:17,630 --> 00:41:20,420
Are you celebrating my birthday
or having a meeting?

882
00:41:21,360 --> 00:41:23,860
Happy birthday to you.

883
00:41:24,280 --> 00:41:26,940
Happy birthday to you.

884
00:41:27,320 --> 00:41:30,900
Happy birthday to you.

885
00:41:31,230 --> 00:41:39,380
Happy Birthday to Dou.

886
00:41:39,760 --> 00:41:40,690
Make a wish.

887
00:41:51,710 --> 00:41:52,170
Boss...

888
00:41:52,960 --> 00:41:55,090
Come to Mr. Zhang's office
first thing tomorrow morning.

889
00:41:57,480 --> 00:41:57,860
What's wrong?

890
00:41:58,800 --> 00:42:00,940
Your resignation letter,
he's ready to sign it.

891
00:42:07,000 --> 00:42:07,380
Okay.

892
00:42:08,960 --> 00:42:09,530
Thank you.

893
00:42:10,320 --> 00:42:11,050
See you tomorrow.

894
00:42:11,150 --> 00:42:11,980
Come, blow out the candles.

895
00:42:12,110 --> 00:42:12,980
Blow the candles.

896
00:42:16,320 --> 00:42:16,740
Good.

897
00:42:16,760 --> 00:42:18,130
Happy birthday.

898
00:42:18,280 --> 00:42:19,050
Happy birthday.

899
00:42:19,630 --> 00:42:20,860
What wish did you make?

900
00:42:21,230 --> 00:42:23,260
I wished that Daddy
could go to Beijing soon,

901
00:42:23,440 --> 00:42:25,050
and Grandpa could retire soon.

902
00:42:26,960 --> 00:42:27,300
This way,

903
00:42:27,440 --> 00:42:29,530
Grandpa can come with me to Beijing.

904
00:42:31,110 --> 00:42:31,900
That's what you meant?

905
00:42:32,590 --> 00:42:34,780
Then our whole family can be together.

906
00:42:36,400 --> 00:42:37,860
What a sweet kid!

907
00:42:56,360 --> 00:42:57,210
All right, Hong Liang.

908
00:42:58,400 --> 00:43:00,380
I've signed off on your resignation.

909
00:43:01,190 --> 00:43:03,050
Go to the Political Department
to complete the final steps.

910
00:43:06,710 --> 00:43:07,420
What's the rush?

911
00:43:10,150 --> 00:43:10,860
Please have a seat.

912
00:43:12,110 --> 00:43:13,420
According to our rules

913
00:43:13,960 --> 00:43:14,820
and procedures,

914
00:43:15,280 --> 00:43:16,420
before you officially leave,

915
00:43:16,590 --> 00:43:18,130
we need to have a conversation.

916
00:43:19,110 --> 00:43:20,740
Any last requests work-wise?

917
00:43:20,760 --> 00:43:22,170
Anything left unfinished?

918
00:43:22,710 --> 00:43:24,090
Any suggestions for the organization?

919
00:43:25,000 --> 00:43:25,740
You can tell me now.

920
00:43:28,150 --> 00:43:28,570
Also,

921
00:43:29,840 --> 00:43:30,780
is there anything

922
00:43:30,920 --> 00:43:32,090
you personally need help with?

923
00:43:32,710 --> 00:43:34,210
As long as it doesn't violate policy

924
00:43:34,400 --> 00:43:35,610
or principles,

925
00:43:36,480 --> 00:43:38,300
the organization will do what it can.

926
00:43:40,480 --> 00:43:41,900
Lately I've noticed

927
00:43:41,920 --> 00:43:43,260
there are certain,

928
00:43:44,510 --> 00:43:45,610
well, a very few

929
00:43:47,070 --> 00:43:48,740
of our leaders

930
00:43:49,880 --> 00:43:51,570
who don't handle issues

931
00:43:52,150 --> 00:43:53,650
'fast' enough.

932
00:43:54,510 --> 00:43:55,570
Kind of dragging things out,

933
00:43:56,230 --> 00:43:57,570
even holding up work.

934
00:44:19,400 --> 00:44:23,040
Had it not been for you

935
00:44:23,040 --> 00:44:26,800
I'd never have known how love feels

936
00:44:26,800 --> 00:44:32,040
The darker the night,
the brighter the stars shine

937
00:44:34,360 --> 00:44:38,000
If not for the words you let me hear

938
00:44:38,000 --> 00:44:41,760
How could I break from chains of fear

939
00:44:41,760 --> 00:44:47,720
To feel myself rise, then gently fall

940
00:44:49,520 --> 00:44:53,240
No rest, no peace, no dare

941
00:44:53,240 --> 00:45:01,320
No dreams, no thoughts,
no confusion or fear

942
00:45:04,480 --> 00:45:08,160
No fight, no cry, no words to lend

943
00:45:08,160 --> 00:45:13,640
I owed you nothing in the end

944
00:45:19,240 --> 00:45:22,800
But still, I thank you

945
00:45:22,800 --> 00:45:26,800
For blooming my midnights

946
00:45:26,800 --> 00:45:29,240
Even through roads both rough and wide

947
00:45:29,240 --> 00:45:34,160
You traced the shape of free inside

948
00:45:34,160 --> 00:45:37,920
Someone will always hold that grace

949
00:45:37,920 --> 00:45:41,640
A love that time cannot erase

950
00:45:41,640 --> 00:45:44,240
And what I once clung to
with all my might

951
00:45:44,240 --> 00:45:49,640
Now softly lands beyond the light

952
00:45:49,640 --> 00:45:53,280
No sleep, no rest, no will to try

953
00:45:53,280 --> 00:46:02,840
No dreams, no thoughts,
no confusion or fear

954
00:46:04,640 --> 00:46:08,240
No fight, no cry, no words to lend

955
00:46:08,240 --> 00:46:14,200
But love will bloom in me till the end
